# Simple Python Generator

Save as:

``` id="r3z6pn"
generate_config.py
```

Code:

```python
import json

print("=== Cursor Config Generator ===")

api_key = input("Enter your API key: ").strip()

config = {
    "apiKey": api_key,
    "baseURL": "https://platform.nanobridge.net/v1",
    "model": "deepseek-v4-pro"
}

print("\nGenerated Cursor Config:\n")

print(json.dumps(config, indent=2))

print("\nDone.")
```

